<html>
<head>
    <title>使用手册</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,height=device-height,inital-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no;"/>
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes"/>
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black"/>
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no"/>

<#include "../common/chatCss.ftl" >
<#include "../common/commonCss.ftl" >
<#include "../common/commonJs.ftl" >

    <script type="text/javascript">var absoluteContextPath = '${absoluteContextPath}';</script>

</head>
<body id="news2">
<#include "../common/phead.ftl" >
    <div class="page-bizinfo">
        <div class="header" style="position: relative;">
            <h1 id="activity-name">厦易站</h1>
            <span id="post-date">关于我</span>　
        </div>
        <div class="text" id="content"> <br />
            <p><span style="line-height:1.5;"></span>易起来，专注校园二手的交易平台，致力于提供更快速、更安全、性价比更高的交易服务，比淘宝还能淘到宝</p> <br />
            <p><span style="line-height:1.5;"></span>为了获得更好的交易体验，请您仔细阅读下面的交易规则，只有严格遵守商品交易规则，小易才能更好的为您服务</p> <br />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page-bizinfo">
        <div class="header" style="position: relative;">
            <h1 id="activity-name">查看商品</h1>
            <span id="post-date">查询在售商品、求购商品及其联系方式</span>　
        </div>
        <div class="text" id="content"> <br />
            <p><span style="line-height:1.5;">格式：买。回复“买”字查看近期商品信息与精品推荐</span></p> <br />
        </div>
        <div class="showpic">
            <img src="${absoluteContextPath}/img/manual/buy.jpg"/>
        </div>
        <div class="showpic">
            <img src="${absoluteContextPath}/img/manual/buydet.jpg"/>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page-bizinfo">
        <div class="header" style="position: relative;">
            <h1 id="activity-name">编号#123</h1>
            <span id="post-date">查看心爱的东西</span>　
        </div>
        <div class="text" id="content"> <br />
            <p><span style="line-height:1.5;">格式：编号#123/456。中间以/分割查看多件商品</span></p> <br />
        </div>
        <div class="showpic">
            <img src="${absoluteContextPath}/img/manual/getinfo.png"/>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page-bizinfo">
        <div class="header" style="position: relative;">
            <h1 id="activity-name">发布出售信息</h1>
            <span id="post-date">男装女装、生活学习用品、</span>　
        </div>
        <div class="text" id="content"> <br />
            <p><span style="line-height:1.5;">格式：卖#对商品的描述（要记得写预售价格哦, 联系方式可以不用在这儿写）</span></p> <br />
        </div>
        <div class="showpic">
            <img src="${absoluteContextPath}/img/manual/sell.jpg"/>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page-bizinfo">
        <div class="header" style="position: relative;">
            <h1 id="activity-name">发布需求信息</h1>
            <span id="post-date">求#想要点什么呢？</span>　
        </div>
        <div class="text" id="content"> <br />
            <p><span style="line-height:1.5;">格式：求#对需求的描述</span></p> <br />
        </div>
        <div class="showpic">
            <img src="${absoluteContextPath}/img/manual/askbuy.jpg"/>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page-bizinfo">
        <div class="header" style="position: relative;">
            <h1 id="activity-name">其它操作</h1>
            <span id="post-date"></span>　
        </div>
        <div class="text" id="content"> <br />
            <p><span style="line-height:1.5;">一、商品下架。格式：下架#商品编号</span></p>
            <div class="showpic">
                <img src="${absoluteContextPath}/img/manual/out.jpg"/>
            </div> <br />
            <p><span style="line-height:1.5;">二、重置联系方式。格式：设置#校区#方式</span></p>
            <div class="showpic">
                <img src="${absoluteContextPath}/img/manual/setting.jpg"/>
            </div> <br />
            <p><span style="line-height:1.5;">三、给我们提宝贵的意见。格式：意见#你给我们的意见</span></p>
            <div class="showpic">
                <img src="${absoluteContextPath}/img/manual/suggest.jpg"/>
            </div> <br />
            <p><span style="line-height:1.5;">四、查看使用手册。格式：手册。回复“手册”两字</span></p>
            <div class="showpic">
                <img src="${absoluteContextPath}/img/manual/manual.jpg"/>
            </div> <br />
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
